comment:
If DC plays it right, they can still outshine the MCU by having films of various Genre. 
The Batman-A crime-mystery-thriller
Aquaman-Classic adventurous
Shazam-Fun, Kiddie friendly, superhero thriller
Wonder Woman-Noir Supernatural Thriller
Wonder Woman-1984-Noir.
The Trench-Horror
DC can have films that are PG Rated as well as films that are R rated..they have a lot of lesser known characters they can use such as Swamp Thing, Constantine, Zatanna, etc. 
And remember, most of the MCU superheroes were relatively unknown compared to Batman and Superman, but Marvel made them household names. DC can do the same with their own heroes.
